	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas, quas domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6130">Ioanni Pontisellę</persName> ad me dedisti, nuper accepi, vir clarissime, easque statim fidelibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l294">Locarnensibus</placeName> reddendas curavi, quo sciant, quid actum sit in comitiis et quomodo se gerere debeant crescente persequtione.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tibi vero fidelium nomine ingentes habeo gratias ob tuam in hoc Christi negotio diligentiam ac sedulitatem.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deus ille cordium servator reddat tibi iuxta misericordiam suam ac animi tui synceritatem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogamus te insuper, domine <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Henrice</persName>, per viscera Christi, ut in ea, quam hilari animo suscepisti, provincia perdures pręvaleasque pręcationibus m. p. ad conditorem, exhortatione ad magistratum, sedulitate vero apud omnes <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinos</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Confidimus enim humanitati tę, quod ultra, quam petimus et oramus, sis ipse facturus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę nunc in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italia</placeName> agitantur, a me paucis intelliges.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ante quatuor dies falsus ad nos pervenerat rumor, nempe <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6724">Petrum Strocium</persName> cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648">Rethis</placeName> omnibus occubuisse; id ad vos quoque permanasse suspicor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed longe alia veritas; nam heri mercatores fide digni ad nos appulerunt nunciantes omnia <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6724">Petri Strocii</persName> ac <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648">Rhetorum</placeName> prospera succedere, multa castella ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hyspanis</placeName> obsessa in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l462">Senensium</placeName> ditione ipso <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6724">Strocio</persName> vi capta, in quibus quadringenti <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hyspani</placeName> trucidati dicuntur multique capti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Populis vero <placeName ref="l1098">Florentinis</placeName> desideratissima libertas promittitur nullisque eorum, quantum fieri potest, iniuria infertur, adeo ut spes sit, non solum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l462">Senenses</placeName> liberari posse, sed etiam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1098">Florentinos</placeName> ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gallum</placeName> defecturos.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736">Pedemontana</placeName> terra planicium omnem obtinent <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galli</placeName> nemine prohibente, Cęsariensium segetes, fenum reliquosque commeatus omnes dirripiunt asportantque et, ut uno verbo dicam, omnia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gallis</placeName> ex voto succedunt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc pauca tibi scribenda censui eaque vera omnia; si quid insuper evenerit memoria dignum, de eodem quoque te certiorem facere conabor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te viri pii dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2336">Bernardinus Occhinus</persName> ac <persName ref="p2019">Augustinus Maynardus</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8022">Niger</persName>.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia domini Iesu Christi cum omnibus vobis.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l93">Clavenę</placeName> 3. idus iulii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Humanitatis tę deditissimum mancipium <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8168">Antonius Marius Besutius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, antistiti <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurino</placeName>, domino meo colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurum</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
